            "content": "/**
 * System Awareness Tools — Squidley's eyes on everything
 * ============================================================
 * These tools don't report. They interpret.
 *
 * The goal: responses that a senior engineer would nod at.
 * Lead with insight, follow with evidence, end with what to do.
